# FlexNetOS Workspace Layout

Task: `T005`

This is a hollow workspace for the fresh `flexnetos` user. The workspace root is not a monorepo, vendor directory, or submodule container.

## Canonical Roots

| Name | Path | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `FLEXNETOS_WORKSPACE` | `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS` | Top-level hollow workspace root. |
| `FLEXNETOS_SRC` | `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src` | Independent peer repository checkouts. |
| `META_ROOT` | `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/meta` | FlexNetOS/meta checkout after T011. |
| `ENVCTL_ROOT` | `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/envctl` | FlexNetOS/envctl checkout after T012. |
| `FLEXNETOS_RUNNER_ROOT` | `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/flexnetos_runner` | FlexNetOS/flexnetos_runner checkout after T013. |

## Repository Placement

Primary FlexNetOS peer repos:

```text
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/meta
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/envctl
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/flexnetos_runner
```

External upstream peer repos, when needed for inspection or pinned source evidence:

```text
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/upstream/<owner>/<repo>
```

Examples:

```text
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/upstream/luccahuguet/yazelix
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/upstream/openai/codex
/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/src/upstream/gitkb/meta
```

Do not vendor upstream source into `meta`, `envctl`, or `flexnetos_runner`. Do not add upstreams as submodules for v0.1.

## State, Cache, Logs, and Release Paths

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/etc` | Reviewed local templates and workspace-level config sources. No raw secrets. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/envctl/tables` | Canonical envctl table storage target. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/codex` | Untracked Codex state root candidate. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/codex/sqlite` | Untracked Codex SQLite state candidate. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/gitkb` | GitKB local state target after GitKB install/init. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/meta` | meta local state/snapshot target. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/lib/runner` | Runner local state/proof target. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/cache/downloads` | Download/cache staging; not source of truth. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/cache/cargo` | Cargo cache target if envctl selects workspace-local Cargo roots. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/cache/kache` | Kache local cache target. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/cache/rtk` | RTK cache/state target. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/cache/yazelix` | Yazelix cache target when envctl owns an override. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/commands` | Command ledger copies or command-specific logs. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/raw` | Raw failure tee logs. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/codex` | Codex logs. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/envctl` | envctl scan/validate/generate logs. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/runner` | runner preflight/build/release logs. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/log/rtk` | RTK logs and raw-output references. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/var/tmp` | Workspace-local temporary files. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/release` | Release output root. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/test-prefix` | Clean install/test prefix root. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/snapshots` | Manual snapshots and metadata. |
| `/home/flexnetos/FlexNetOS/artifacts` | Non-release intermediate artifacts. |

## Rules

- Peer repos remain independent Git repositories.
- The workspace root must not track peer repo contents.
- Generated runtime files are artifacts and must declare their envctl source table and checksum.
- Raw secrets are forbidden in this workspace.
