                    "subject": " - [User-Defined Type Function Syntax](https://github.com/luau-lang/rfcs/blob/12a39c3fdb6e0b29a4e44ac2ffcf66c8fe3173e9/docs/user-defined-type-functions.md)  - Anticipatory support for the [read](https://github.com/luau-lang/rfcs/blob/0280f4fbf266687bf4b4186b774916b4e3638543/docs/property-readonly.md) and [write](https://github.com/luau-lang/rfcs/blob/0280f4fbf266687bf4b4186b774916b4e3638543/docs/property-writeonly.md) keywords  - *Potentially compatibility breaking*: Reversed the specification order of logical sections of highlight queries where priority matters. New helix versions seem to have a contradistinctive priority scheme which affects this project.  - Other minor changes"
