The gate is green, but the markdown summary exposed a quality issue: a few nested JSON fields were being read with optimistic key names, so they rendered as `None`/empty even though the source artifacts have the evidence. I’m correcting those mappings before I call this done; green proof is necessary, but the artifact should be pleasant to trust too.
